# Spot the Ball inpainted output. The inpaint script writes here as
# a local staging copy before scp'ing to the Lightsail box, which
# serves the files at api.mob.tennis/spot-the-ball/. They aren't
# part of the Vercel build any more.
web/public/spot-the-ball/

